-- Konami to Acquire Pachinko-Slot-Machine Maker Abilit in Stock Transaction
-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 2010-09-21T07:07:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/konami-to-acquire-pachinko-slot-machine-maker-abilit-in-stock-transaction.html
Konami Corp., a Japanese video game
developer, will acquire Abilit Corp. in a stock transaction on
Jan. 1.  Konami will offer 0.052 share for each in the pachinko-
slot-machine maker, according to a statement to the Tokyo Stock
Exchange today. Abilit shares will be delisted on Dec. 28.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyung Bok Cho at 
 kcho7@bloomberg.net  